              <link itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" href="https://discuss.redash.io/t/lock-the-headers-in-the-query-results-when-you-scroll-down/3493">


              <span class="crawler-post-infos">
                  <time itemprop='datePublished' datetime='2020-03-25T15:54:53Z' class='post-time'>
                    March 25, 2020,  3:54pm
